@startuml
autonumber

actor "Gebruiker" as user

box "MVVM Architectuur" #LightGray
    participant "View\n(XAML Page)" as view
    participant "ViewModel\n(CommunityToolkit.Mvvm)" as vm
    participant "Model / DTO" as model
end box

box "Service Laag" #LightBlue
    participant "Service\n(HttpClient / DI)" as service
end box

box "Backend" #LightGreen
    participant "ASP.NET Core\nWeb API" as api
    participant "Database\n(SQLite / EF Core)" as db
end box

== Data Binding (View - ViewModel) ==

user -> view: Interactie (klik, typ, etc.)
view -> vm: Data Binding (x:DataType, {Binding})
note right: Compiled bindings via\nx:DataType in XAML

== Command Execution (ViewModel) ==

vm -> vm: [RelayCommand] of property setter
note right: CommunityToolkit.Mvvm\nsource generators
vm -> service: Aanroep service (await Get/Post)

== Service - Backend ==

service -> api: HTTP request (GET/POST/DELETE)\nmet JWT Bearer token
api -> db: EF Core query (Entity Framework)
db --> api: Resultaat
api --> service: JSON response (Resource DTO)

== Data Flow Terug (ObservableProperty) ==

service --> vm: Gedeserialiseerde data
vm -> vm: Update [ObservableProperty]
note right: Roept PropertyChanged\nevent aan
vm -> view: Automatische UI-update\nd.m.v. data binding
view -> user: Weergave nieuwe data

== Offline / Lokale Opslag ==

alt Offline modus (geen internet)
    service --> vm: Exception (geen verbinding)
    vm -> vm: Val terug op lokale opslag
    note right: LocalDatabaseService\n(SQLite via sqlite-net-pcl)
    vm -> model: Lokaal opslaan\nmet IsSynced = false
    model --> vm: Opgeslagen
    vm -> view: Toon lokale data in UI
end

@enduml
